name: CurverCRVVoterProxy
description: This vault accepts deposits of rCRV tokens obtained by supplying either ETH or rETH to the liquidity pool on Curve here. rCRV tokens are staked in the gauge on Curve to earn CRV and FIS rewards. Rewards are swapped for one of the underlying assets and resupplied to the liquidity pool to obtain more rCRV.
